				<header class="special container">
					<!-- Just commented the icon, could be added again
					<span class="icon fa-bar-chart-o"></span>
					-->
					<h3><strong>Forsolar</strong> project is about short-term solar radiation forecasts
					<br />
					in real time, solving challenges on solar applications power grid-integration.</h3>
					<p>
					<br />
					Solar power applications are sensitive to short-time variability in terms of minutes to local weather conditions - a real issue to integrate your rooftop panel in the (smart) grid... - for which very few forecasting solutions exist. 
					<br />
					As Forsolar Association, we developped a portable,  forecasting prototype that can be deployed near the solar power facilities.</p>
					
					<!--					
					<p>The project started in 2014 after winning the <strong>Total's Bourse Air</strong>,
					<br />
					attributed to innovative projects in solar energy sector. 
					<br />
					Forsolar project is develo</p>
					-->
				</header>
					
				<!-- One -->
					<section class="wrapper style2 container special-alt">
						<div class="row half">
							<div class="9u">
							
								<header>
									<h2>Our stand-alone <strong>Forsolar-Pseries</strong> prototype integrates sensory and processing equipment. <p>All is fully automated.</p></h2>
								</header>
								<p>Pseries combines <strong>real-time monitoring</strong> of sensory data (high-resolution all-sky cloud imagery) and <strong>real-time processing</strong>. </p>
<p>Forecastings and data accessible online in a <strong>secure</strong> username and password HTTPS protected webpage accessible via internet in any device (smartphone, tablet or PC).</p> 
<p>All data is uploaded to a <strong>cloud</strong>, for posterior access.</p> 
									</ul>
								<footer>
									<ul class="buttons">
										<li><a href="#" class="button">Find Out More</a></li>
