					<section class="wrapper style1 container special">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="4u">
							
								<section>
									<span class="icon featured fa-check"></span>
									<header>
										<h3>Reliable and Low-Cost</h3>
									</header>
									<p>Integrating high realibility and weatherproof sensory from insolation, humidity, temperature and high-resolution all-sky color imagery, Pseries is a weatherproof, specially conceived prototype at low-cost.</p>
								</section>
							
							</div>
							<div class="4u">
							
								<section>
									<span class="icon featured fa-check"></span>
									<header>
										<h3>Readiness: Forecasts via HTTPS</h3>
									</header>
									<p>The real-time monitoring and forecasting data is easily accessible via internet in a HTTPS page protected by username and password. This allows for the data to be accessible in any type of smartphone or tablet with considerable security. </p>
								</section>
							
							</div>
							<div class="4u">
							
								<section>
									<span class="icon featured fa-check"></span>
									<header>
										<h3>Availability: Data in the Cloud</h3>
									</header>
									<p>Acquired data and processed data is only temporarly kept in the prototype, being soon uploaded consistently to an online cloud. This allows users to access previous data in their personal computer or other device.</p>
								</section>
							
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>
					
